          Toledo Technologies provides software development services including but not 
          limited to bug fixes, feature development, automation, and codebase sales. 
          Specific terms for any services will be outlined in separate agreements 
          between Toledo Technologies and the client.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        
