          For custom development work, intellectual property ownership and licensing 
          will be defined in the specific project agreement. Generally, clients receive 
          full ownership of custom work upon payment.
        </p>
        
        <h3>Codebases</h3>
        <p>
          Purchased codebases are licensed to the buyer as specified in the purchase 
          agreement. Standard licenses grant perpetual, non-exclusive rights to use, 
          modify, and deploy the code.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Use of the Site</h2>
        <p>You agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the Site for any unlawful purpose</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Site</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the Site or servers</li>
          <li>Transmit viruses or malicious code</li>
          <li>Collect user information without consent</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Contact Form and Communications</h2>
        <p>
          When you submit information through our contact form, you grant us permission 
          to contact you regarding your inquiry. We will not add you to marketing lists 
          without explicit consent.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>
          The Site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express 
          or implied. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted, secure, 
          or error-free.
        </p>
        <p>
          Information on this Site is for general informational purposes. While we 
          strive for accuracy, we make no representations about the completeness or 
          accuracy of information on the Site.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          Toledo Technologies shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, 
          consequential, or punitive damages resulting from your use of or inability 
          to use the Site.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          The Site may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible 
          for the content or practices of these external sites. Linking to external 
          sites does not imply endorsement.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Indemnification</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Toledo Technologies from any claims, 
          damages, or expenses arising from your use of the Site or violation of these 
          Terms.
        </p>
        
